Description:
Fantastic Modern Lifestyle with Amazing Bay Views
A fantastic opportunity for a showpiece modern lifestyle is now available on the 11th floor of this near new 883-889 Collins St address. This luxury 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom apartment, located on this prestigious location right in the heart of Victoria Harbour is something you should never miss out.
With fantastic bay views on the Southern side of the South Tower, 1105S comprises spacious open plan lounge and dining zone, full glass sliding door opens to a generous sized balcony maximising the beautiful views of Port Phillip Bay. Gourmet L-shaped kitchen fully equipped with Miele appliances and stone benchtop.
Master bedroom with full ensuite and WIRs and second double bedroom opposite the main bathroom, and both complimented with the lovely Southern light, plus cupboard Euro laundry.
Extra features include polished timber floor boards, floor to ceiling windows, split system air-conditioning, intercom system, and a security car park.
You will also be spoiled by accessing the 20m swimming pool, cinema, billiards room, yoga, gym, BBQ, private dining room and resident lounge.
The new 889 Collins St Building also offers a complete range of waterfront living with prime views of Melbourne CBD and Yarra River and this exclusive address is within walking distance to Etihad Stadium, Melbourne Convention and Exhibition Centre, DFO South Wharf Shopping Mall, Crown Casino, Southern Cross Station and countless numbers of cafes, restaurants and shops, not to mention the free tram lines that will take you to Central CBD within minutes down Collins St.
Inspection By Appointment.

Description:
DON'T MISS OUT
Located in Melbourne's famous Docklands and situated on the 14th floor, this immaculate superb apartment has it all with uninterrupted views of the city skyline and northern suburbs, restaurants, CBD and tram at your doorstep and all the entertainment that Docklands has to offer.
Designed to capitalize on light and space your new home features floor-to-ceiling windows to make the most of the morning sun and views and fresh air.
This beautifully designed open planned apartment boasts a large air-conditioned living area which opens onto an entertainer's balcony with uninterrupted views to Melbourne CBD and is serviced by a modern up to the minute classical timber kitchen fitted with stone bench tops, premium European style appliances and timber floors throughout.
Sleeping accommodations is enhanced by a large bedroom with fully fitted Built-in-Robes, large and fully tiled bathroom with double shower and, built-in washing machine and clothes drier and security parking.
What better way to wake up in the morning? Make the most of watching the rising sun with the city skyline as your backdrop while having breakfast/coffee on your balcony.
This exceptional first-home buyer opportunity or investment also includes indoor pool and sauna PLUS a state-of-the-art gym with stunning views and massive outdoor park with BBQ facilities.
Don't forget the tram stop at the doorstep including the Free City Circle, short stroll to Marvel Stadium, Southern Cross Station and a variety of vibrant restaurants and retail outlets.
INSPECTIONS STRICTLY BY APPOINTMENT
For inspection contact Charles Marvelli 0423 530 172

Description:
Magnificent harbour views and relaxed open living
With the promise of a Harbour aspect which means you get to enjoy striking views of the scenic Victoria Harbour whenever you feel like, this sizeable and well-designed two bedroom Palladio apartment has so much appeal plus a fantastic NewQuay precinct location.
Make the most of a well-sized central living zone with separate spaces for lounge and dining, undercover balcony with appealing views of the iconic harbour, tasteful kitchen with a breakfast counter for meals on the go and stainless steel appliances, both light filled bedrooms with built-in robes, and a well-appointed bathroom with a bath/shower combo.
Also enjoy a European laundry, reverse cycle heating and cooling, additional heating, secure intercom, secure car space, and access to a health club with rooftop pool, gym, and private function area. Caravel Lane is a fantastic location where you have access to nearby restaurants including Mint-o-Mustard, Docklands Pizzeria, Renzos Bar, and Bhoj Restaurant. Youre also near The District Docklands, Marvel Stadium, IGA X-Press supermarket, Moonee Ponds Creek Trail, and trams on Harbour Esplanade and Docklands Drive.

A statement of style and sophistication with spectacular harbour scenery
Capturing a picture-perfect postcard view stretching from Victoria Harbour through to Port Phillip Bay, and enriched by an exhilarating lifestyle location, this Palladio two-bedroom apartment delivers modern indoor-outdoor living in spacious luxury. Affording outstanding residents facilities, and surrounded by cafés, restaurants, bars, shopping and entertainment, while just a leisurely stroll or tram ride to the CBD, enjoy life the way its meant to be lived!
Enjoying a relaxing space that caters to laidback daily living, social dining and vibrant entertaining with its dazzling backdrop view by night, the open plan domain spills onto a private balcony for alfresco enjoyment. A sleek modern kitchen easily caters to the masses, offering a full-appointment of Omega appliances amid an unusually abundant expanse of storage for todays apartment lifestyles.
Providing two large bedrooms with wall-to-wall robing, a central bathroom and European laundry, the home is completed with todays favourite comforts and security including split system air-conditioning, secure video intercom and swipe entry and basement parking. Benefitting from its outstanding picturesque location, residents can enjoy resort-style facilities with breathtaking views including a grassy communal area with a herb and veggie garden, a business conference room, a rooftop pool and garden, and gymnasium.

Blessed with brilliant space both inside and out, this fantastic 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom Nolan apartment is a modern delight.

Both bedrooms are also equipped with built-in robe storage including the well-sized 2nd bedroom.
The kitchen which looks out onto the central living hub is splashed with luxury black benchtops, a breakfast counter, and stainless steel appliances, while just next door is the stylish bathroom which has a separate shower and bath. Other features include European laundry, ducted heating and cooling, additional heating, secure intercom, secure car space, and access to a pool, gym, and entertaining area.
In the heart of the NewQuay Precinct, youll have access to an array of amazing local eateries including Renzos Bar Café Italiano, Oscars Table, and Bhoj restaurant just to name a few. Youre also near The District Docklands, IGA supermarket, Moonee Ponds Creek Trail, Ron Barassi Snr Park, and trams to West Preston, Bundoora RMIT, CBD, and beyond.
To arrange an inspection, please contact Charles Finnigan 0437 204 556 or Vicky Leong on 0452 486 860.

Heritage Grand Central
Enjoy the absolute splendor as you enter the iconic Grand Central building with security entrance and lift access to this spacious fourth level two bedroom apartment.
Featuring a most spacious living and dining area with large windows and an adjoining well appointed kitchen with quality appliances and cabinetry. The upper level comprises two spacious loft style bedrooms both with built in robes and serviced by a stylish central bathroom and separate toilet. Additional features include central heating/cooling, Euro Style laundry and resident access to the resort style facilities including heated pool, spa, gym and barbecue area.
A totally convenient location to all this wonderful city of Melbourne has to offer with passing tram, close Southern Cross Station, Collins Street, restaurants, sporting facilities, entertainment, Crown Casino, Southbank Promenade, Docklands precinct and so much more.

Description:
Light-filled and opulent Gold Tower apartment
Flawless from head to toe, enjoying fantastic natural light thanks to the northerly aspect, and a superb opportunity for first home buyers and investors, this 1 bedroom apartment is affordable Docklands luxury.
Enjoys fantastic sun through the relaxed living and meals zone
North-facing balcony promises views of the Melbourne Star Observation Wheel
Functional stone kitchen accessed just off the entry features premium appliances
Bedroom with BIR is also north-facing and enjoys fantastic views
Designer black tapware through chic bathroom which has a rain shower
European laundry, split system heating and cooling
Intercom entry in the secure Gold Tower complex
AMENITIES
The Gold Tower which is part of the Aqui development enjoys 25m indoor pool, spa, sauna, gym, library, private meeting rooms, and rooftop garden.
LOCATION
Spend lazy weekends strolling the charming waterfront where you can enjoy lunch at Cargo, Berth, and Fish Bar just to name a few. The District Docklands is also a highlight of this NewQuay precinct, with this complex offering Hoyts Cinemas, 8 Street hawker food outlets, and a new fresh food precinct opening soon called The Market which will offer an array of butchers, delis, bakeries, coffee roasters, Woolworths supermarket, and Dan Murphys. Youre also in close proximity to Marvel Stadium, Victoria Harbour precinct, Capital City Trail for bike riders, trams taking you all across Melbourne, and Southern Cross Station.

Description:
Breathtaking Penthouse Views and Sleek Style
Perched magnificently on the 32nd floor of The Quays complex which offers some of the best building facilities in the Docklands, this outstanding one bedroom penthouse level apartment delivers spectacular views and modern class.
Enjoy the best one bedroom views in Docklands
Vistas including the city skyline, Marvel Stadium, Victoria Harbour, Dandenong Ranges and Port Phillip Bay
Relaxed living with designated areas for carpeted lounge and tiled meals
High spec Miele kitchen with stainless steel appliances
Bedroom with BIR and access out to the balcony
Mosaic tiles add a touch of designer flair to the bathroom
European laundry, reverse cycle heating and cooling
Secure car space
AMENITIES
The Quays features a Health Club with a pool, spa, sauna, gym and yoga studio, Residents Club on Level One with a library, reading room, business centre, boardroom, private dining room & cinema lounge plus a rooftop garden with NewQuays only Tennis Court, BBQ and dining facilities. The addition of a new concierge at the buildings entry caps off the thoughtful and all-inclusive amenities.
LOCATION
Youre situated right on the edge of the NewQuay precinct which also gives you convenient access to Digital Harbour, Stadium precinct, and Victoria Harbour precinct. The District Docklands is only a short walk and delivers a Hoyts Cinemas, amazing 8 Street hawker food outlets, and a new fresh food precinct opening soon called The Market which will offer an array of butchers, delis, bakeries, coffee roasters, Woolworths supermarket, and Dan Murphys. Youre also close to restaurants including Woolshed, Mama Rumaan, and Mill & Bakery, Marvel Stadium, Capital City Trail, nearby trams including the free City Circle line, Southern Cross Station, and Skybus.
Please contact Thomas Tregonning on 0413 317 304 to arrange an exclusive viewing.

Description:
To a Tee at Aqui
Brilliant North West facing apartment nestled in the Aqui Promenade residential complex, designed by award winning architects Woods Bagot.
Located on the 10th floor, this spacious 1 bedroom has so much to offer.
Open plan dining and living area adjoins a fantastic undercover balcony perfect for relaxing.
Modern galley kitchen with integrated stainless steel Miele appliances including gas stove top and oven. Plenty of storage space highlighted by a maroon feature panel.
Stylish bedroom with mirrored built in robes, also with floor to ceiling windows.
Fully tiled bathroom with maroon coloured tiled feature wall matching the scheme of the kitchen.
Other features include: Split system air conditioner, floorboards in the main traffic area and carpeted bedroom, modern black tapware, timber veneer detailing, and stone benchtops.
Complex features include: 25m swimming pool, gymnasium, onsite manager, security entrance, business/study meeting area, communal BBQ and landscaped rooftop garden.
Located close to District Docklands shopping precinct, new Hoyts Cinema, O'Brien ice rink and Ron Barassi Snr park. Free tram zoned, close to Southern Cross Station, and easy access to the freeway system.
Invest now and move in later!
Call Eugene Louey on 0401 299 997.
